Videos upload:
			Case 1 'AVI video upload'
Open application main page
Perform login
	-'upload media' button should be present
Click on 'upload media' button
	-'upload media' pop-up should appear
Copy 'testfile1.avi' to 'upload media pop-up
	-'upload media' pop-up should disappear
	-'successful media upload' notification should be displayed
Click on 'My videos' tab from left sidebar menu
	-previously loaded videos thumbnails should be shown
	-testfile1.avi' thumbnail  should be listed in top left corner of videos list 

			Case 2 'MOV video upload'
Open application main page
Perform login
	-'upload media' button should be present
Click on 'upload media' button
	-'upload media' pop-up should appear
Copy 'testfile2.mov' to 'upload media pop-up
	-'upload media' pop-up should disappear
	-'successful media upload' notification should be displayed
Click on 'My videos' tab from left sidebar menu
	-previously loaded videos thumbnails should be shown
	-testfile2.mov' thumbnail  should be listed in top left corner of videos list 

