			Case 4 'WEBM image upload'
Open application main page
Perform login
	-'upload media' button should be present
Click on 'upload media' button
	-'upload media' pop-up should appear
Copy 'testfile4.webm' to 'upload media pop-up
	-'upload media' pop-up should not dissapear
	-'ERROR: only avi,mkv and mov video types are allowed' notification should be displayed
Click on 'My videos' tab from left sidebar menu
	-previously loaded videos thumbnails should be shown
	-testfile4.webm' thumbnail should not be listed in top left corner of videos list


